The paper deals with audiovisual integration and computational modeling of cross-modal representations, which are topics that are commonly studied in the fields of speech and image processing, computer vision, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
